title: YouTube usage penetration in the United States 2019 , by age group
summary: In general Reach has fallen over the Year.
Reach is roughly constant from 36-45_years to 46-55_years, and finally slightly decreasing from 46-55_years to 56+_years.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 46-55_years and 56+_years.
The highest Reach, of value 67.0 was reached at Year 36-45_years
Minimum Reach about 58.0 was reached at Year 56+_years
